### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Agent config
GET http://localhost:8000/api/models/agent/config
Accept: application/json

### Agent run
POST http://localhost:8000/api/models/agent/runs
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Idempotency-Key: agent-demo-1

{
  "client_request_id": "front-agent-1",
  "region_id": "novosibirsk_oblast",
  "sim_params": {
    "pop_size": 100000,
    "pop_infected": 10,
    "forecast_days": 45,
    "beta": 0.02
  },
  "interventions": [
    {"date": "2020-03-20", "beta_change": 0.7}
  ]
}

### ML config
GET http://localhost:8000/api/models/ml-forecast/config
Accept: application/json

### ML run
POST http://localhost:8000/api/models/ml-forecast/runs
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Idempotency-Key: ml-demo-1

{
  "client_request_id": "front-ml-1",
  "region_id": "spb",
  "context_date": "2024-03-06",
  "model_ids": ["seir_hcd", "lstm", "cgan"],
  "indicator_id": "new_diagnoses",
  "mode": "compare_models"
}

### MFG result
GET http://localhost:8000/api/models/mfg/scenario-results?region_id=novosibirsk_oblast&period_id=period1&strategy_id=base
Accept: application/json
